Basic Fare details
Base Fare is 40
Rate per Kilometer is 10

User input for distance
Enter the Distance traveled (in kilometers)

Fare Calculation

If the value of the entered distance (in km) is 0, 1
The Total Fare should be Base Fare only
The Extra Kilometer is 0

If it is not 0 then 
The Extra Kilometer should be Distance - 1
The Total Fare should be = Base Fare + (Extra Kilometer * Rate Per Kilometer)

OUTPUT

Base Fare
Rate per Kilometer = 40
Distance Traveled = 10
Extra Kilometer = ?
Total Fare = ?

